## Supported File Types

| Format | Extensions | Max Size | OCR Support |
|--------|-----------|----------|-------------|
| PDF (Text) | .pdf | 100 MB | No |
| PDF (Scanned) | .pdf | 100 MB | Yes |
| Word Document | .docx | 100 MB | No |
| Excel Spreadsheet | .xlsx | 100 MB | No |
| CSV Data | .csv | 100 MB | No |
| PNG Image | .png | 100 MB | Yes |
| JPEG Image | .jpg, .jpeg | 100 MB | Yes |
| TIFF Image | .tiff, .tif | 100 MB | Yes |
| XML Data | .xml | 100 MB | No |

---

## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| Backend Framework | FastAPI | REST API server |
| Server | Uvicorn | ASGI server |
| Database | SQLite + SQLAlchemy | Data persistence |
| PDF Processing | PyMuPDF | PDF text extraction |
| Word Processing | python-docx | DOCX extraction |
| Excel Processing | openpyxl, pandas | Spreadsheet processing |
| OCR Engine | Tesseract + pytesseract | Image text extraction |
| Image Processing | OpenCV, Pillow | Image manipulation |
| Embeddings | Sentence-Transformers (MiniLM) | 384d vector generation |
| Similarity Search | scikit-learn (cosine) | Semantic matching |
| LLM | Groq (llama-3.1-8b-instant) | AI response generation |
| NLP | NLTK, langdetect | Text processing |
| Logging | Loguru | Application logging |
| Frontend | HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript | User interfaces |

---

## API Endpoints

### Document Management
- POST /documents/upload — Upload and auto-process documents
- GET /documents — List all documents
- GET /documents/{id} — Get document details
- DELETE /documents/{id} — Delete document
- GET /documents/{id}/chunks — View document chunks
- GET /documents/{id}/metadata — View extracted metadata
- GET /documents/search?q= — Semantic search

### AI Copilot
- POST /copilot/chat — Chat with AI (RAG)
- GET /copilot/health — Health check

### Knowledge Graph
- GET /kg/query?q= — Search graph
- GET /kg/equipment — List all equipment
- GET /kg/documents — List all documents

### Root Cause Analysis
- GET /rca/analyze/{equipment_id} — Full failure analysis
- GET /rca/quick/{equipment_id} — Quick root cause summary

