## Judging Criteria Alignment

### Innovation (25%)
RAG + Knowledge Graph + Root Cause Analysis in a single platform. 9-format ingestion with automatic OCR. Smart chunking for tabular data. Equipment-aware AI that understands industrial terminology.

### Business Impact (25%)
$177K-$806K annual savings per facility. 99.8% faster document retrieval. 35% productivity improvement. Zero-cost AI inference. Prevents knowledge loss from retiring workforce.

### Technical Excellence (20%)
384-dimensional vector embeddings. Cosine similarity semantic search. Groq LLM integration. Smart chunking algorithm. Modular microservices architecture. REST API for integration.

### Scalability (15%)
REST API enables integration with SAP, Maximo, and other systems. Modular services can be deployed independently. SQLite to PostgreSQL migration path. Docker-ready architecture.

### User Experience (15%)
Drag-and-drop upload. Natural language chat interface. Dark theme with professional design. Responsive for desktop, tablet, and mobile. Zero training required.

